ctica.ac.uk/family_liaison/mail.php |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2014-01-28 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203095235/http://www.antarctica.ac.uk/family_liaison/mail.php |archivedate=3 February 2014 |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n* [[BVI Post]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bvi.gov.vg/departments/bvi-post-0|title=BVI Post  - Government of the Virgin Islands|publisher=[[Government of the British Virgin Islands]]|website=www.bvi.gov.vg|accessdate=6 April 2018}}</ref>\n* [[Cayman Islands]] Postal Service<ref>{{cite web|title=Cayman Islands Postal Service|url=http://www.caymanpost.gov.ky|publisher=[[Government of the Cayman Islands]]|accessdate=7 July 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Falklands]] Post Service Limited<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.falklandstamps.com/|title=Falklands South Georgia BAT Stamps|publisher=[[Falkland Islands Government]]|website=Falklands South Georgia BAT Stamps|accessdate=17 July 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://digilander.libero.it/fabioalarici/f.html|title=Postal Authorities F|website=digilander.libero.it|accessdate=14 July 2017}}</ref>\n* [[Guernsey Post]]\n* [[Isle of Man Post Office]]\n* [[Jersey Post]]\n* [[Montserrat]] General Post Office<ref>{{cite web|url=http://digilander.libero.it/fabioalarici/m.html|title=Postal Authorities M|website=digilander.libero.it|accessdate=14 July 2017}}</ref>\n* [[Pitcairn]] Post Office<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stamps.gov.pn/|title=Pitcairn Islands Philatelic Bureau|website=www.stamps.gov.pn|accessdate=14 July 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://digilander.libero.it/fabioalarici/o-p.html|title=Postal Authorities O-P|website=digilander.libero.it|accessdate=14 July 2017}}</ref>\n* [[Royal Gibraltar Post Office]]\n* [[Turks and Caicos Post Office]] <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tcimall.tc/government/|title=Government - Turks and Caicos Information - TCI Mall|website=www.tcimall.tc|accessdate=14 July 2017}}</ref>\n* [[Saint Helena, Ascension and Tristan da Cunha]]:\n** [[Ascension Po